title: Wo Jian Qile Yi Di Shuxing
overview: Feng Xia, a game cheat master known as the Liver Emperor, crosses over to a world of immortal cultivation where the spiritual energy is in decline, and with his golden fingers of attributes and strategic experience cultivated in the game, he defeats numerous powerful enemies and gains numerous skills along the way. In order to keep the peace of this world, Feng Xia and the Dusty Sea Ancestor join hands to kill the gods and guard the peace of the world; however, the Dusty Sea Ancestor unfortunately died as a result, in order to find a way to bring the Dusty Sea Ancestor back to life, Feng Xia finally set out to become a god.
